models

Class NamedFieldMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.NamedFieldMatrix

  • public class NamedFieldMatrix
extends Object
    A dynamically resizing two-dimensional Array whose fields can be adressed by pairs of Strings as well as pairs of numbers. Supports output to a csv-Table and can be read from a csv-Table.
